      "standard_deduction": "Per filing status. Subtracted from gross income before bracket lookup. Updated annually by IRS for inflation. 2025 values currently loaded.",
      "niit": "Net Investment Income Tax. 3.8% applied to investment income (dividends, cap gains, interest) above AGI threshold ($250k MFJ, $200k single). Threshold is NOT inflation-adjusted by statute — it has been $250k since 2013.",
