      "brackets_format": "List of {up_to, rate} objects, same structure as federal. up_to: null = top bracket.",
      "how_to_set_state": "State is NOT set in this file. Set per-profile in person.json (state field) or defaulted to the profile's home state in api.py.",
      "standard_deduction": "Most states have their own standard deduction separate from federal. Some states use federal AGI as the starting point instead."
